   7:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/per/i2c.h **** /** A handle for interacting with an I2C peripheral. This is a dumb
   8:../libs/PoliTeKDSP/libs/libDaisy/src/per/i2c.h ****  *  gateway that internally points to one of the four I2C peripherals
